| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-4456 — Recovery Inhibition (bianlian)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: f3111d7a-d116-5e79-9eb4-9fe8e87519f0"
